	(text_box "Voltage divider to set TADJ pin for optimum performance depening on frequency.\n\nFor first prototype, a trimmer is included to allow precise tuning.\nTrimmer at minimum: 0.8018V\nTrimmer at maximum: 0.8713V\n\nThis allows tuning between 900MHz & 1.9MHz from table 4 in datasheet (see inset)."
